embeddedItem.name: Wubbaboo
embeddedItem.desc: Avatar reward obtained from finishing the mission "Requiem Mass."
embeddedItem.lore:
As Astral Spirits contained by the Department of Ecology, it took a lot of effort to teach Wubbaboos to look at the camera.

"Here, look here. Wooo wooo. Wooo whooo wooo? Did you get it?"
